Step 1 (Create Telegram action type)

- Create type in `shared/src/types` as in example bellow

```ts
export interface TgAction {
  userId: number;
  username: string;
  botName: string;
  type: 'command' | 'callback' | 'message';
  name: string;
  data: Record<string, string>;
  createdAt: Date;
}
```

Step 2 (Create database model)

- Use `.cursor/rules/backend/database/create-model.mdc` rules to create database model from type `TgAction`
